sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant Frontend
    participant Backend
    participant Auth
    participant Controller
    participant DB

    Admin->>Frontend: Create/Update/Delete product
    Frontend->>Backend: POST/PUT/DELETE /api/products (Bearer)
    Backend->>Auth: Validate token + admin
    Auth-->>Backend: Authorized
    Backend->>Controller: manageProduct
    Controller->>DB: Save/Delete product
    DB-->>Controller: OK
    Controller-->>Backend: 200/201 response
    Backend-->>Frontend: Success JSON
    Frontend-->>Admin: Catalogue updated
